OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAfter a locally grey and
OL,6,Fmisty start Thursday will be another
OL,7,Ffine day for many with warm sunny
OL,8,Fspells. However, there is a chance of
OL,9,Fthe odd light shower developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FIt will
OL,12,Fstay fine on Friday, with further
OL,13,Fspells of warm sunshine. Over the
OL,14,Fweekend the weather looks more mixed
OL,15,Fwith some rain developing at times,
OL,16,Fand becoming breezy too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
